  "detailed_description": "<strong>Beardy the Digger</strong> is an exciting adventure in atmospheric locations that will allow you to discover the genre of platformer from a new perspective. Take a trip to uncharted gloomy dungeons, to the dangerous foot of the mountain, overcome various obstacles on the way to the main goal to return home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/52bd70b416a9eab4246af227d7d12d2d.avif?t=1709660690\" width=600 height=400 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features of the game</h2><br>   <strong>Diverse gameplay</strong>, which includes puzzles, passing levels on speed and reaction. You shall not forget potions with an unexpected effect!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/c29c46e60abebc17514ebd1d562c1f81.poster.avif?t=1709660690\" width=600 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/c29c46e60abebc17514ebd1d562c1f81.webm?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/c29c46e60abebc17514ebd1d562c1f81.mp4?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>   <strong>Various locations</strong>, mysterious dungeons, roaring fjords and many others;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/2cdad8286663cf748aa11f47082ff379.poster.avif?t=1709660690\" width=600 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/2cdad8286663cf748aa11f47082ff379.webm?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/2cdad8286663cf748aa11f47082ff379.mp4?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>   <strong>Colourful graphics</strong>, embodied with the latest technology from Unity 2019 to create a warm lamp light;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/bd05079c338f69a83b1c4af7a7c9af5a.poster.avif?t=1709660690\" width=600 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/bd05079c338f69a83b1c4af7a7c9af5a.webm?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/bd05079c338f69a83b1c4af7a7c9af5a.mp4?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>   <strong>Sound effects</strong>, immersed in an atmosphere of adventure and danger.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/8e75350d03089462df31e2a706f51b46.poster.avif?t=1709660690\" width=600 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/8e75350d03089462df31e2a706f51b46.webm?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144630/extras/8e75350d03089462df31e2a706f51b46.mp4?t=1709660690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
